==English==

===Noun===
'''boast'''
# A [[brag]], a loud appraisal of oneself
# {{squash}} A shot where the ball is [[drive]]n off a side wall and then strikes the front wall

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[omakehu]] (1)

===Verb===
'''boast'''
# to [[brag]]; to talk loudly in praise of oneself
# (''squash'') To play a boast shot

